      "value": "<p>You gain a +10-foot status bonus to your Speed until the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>While you have a status bonus to at least one of your Speeds, your Strikes with this scimitar that deal fire damage gain a +2 status bonus to their fire damage. The status bonus increases to +3 if the weapon has a greater striking rune and +4 for major striking.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><em>Note: the base +2 increase to damage is included in this effect. It cannot currently be made to automatically increase.</em></p>"
